<Body>
	<Title>永胜发生特大车祸  轿车和摩托车相撞 造成3死两伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007年07月13日 09:47</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>
                <Event eid="e1"><Time type="relTime" tid="t1">10日晚9时30分</Time>,<Location lid="l1">永胜县境内的祥（云）宁（蒗）公路线二级公路教基田路段</Location>发生<Object sid="s1">轿车</Object>和<Object sid="s1">摩托车</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d1">相撞</Denoter>的特大交通事故</Event>，
                造成<Event eid="e2"><Participant sid="s2">3人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d2">死亡</Denoter></Event>、
                <Event eid="e3"><Participant sid="s3">两人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d3">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
                <Sentence>这是<Event eid="e4" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s4">记者</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t4">昨日</Time>从丽江市永胜县新闻办<Denoter type="perception" did="d4">了解</Denoter>到的</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e5" type="thoughtevent">据<Participant sid="s5">永胜县交警大队</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d5">介绍</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e6"><Time type="relTime" tid="t6">当晚</Time>，永胜县一信用社职员<Participant sid="s6">李某</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d6">驾驶</Denoter><Object sid="s6">轿车</Object>载着3人</Event>，
                <Event eid="e7">从<Location lid="l7">期纳公路线</Location><Denoter type="movement" did="d7">开往</Denoter><Location lid="l7">程海镇</Location>方向</Event>，
                <Event eid="e8"><Time type="relTime" tid="t8">9时30分</Time>,当<Object sid="s8">车</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d8">行</Denoter>至<Location lid="l8">祥宁线二级路教基田路段</Location></Event>时，
                <Event eid="e9">与驶来的程某驾驶的<Object sid="s9">一辆摩托车</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d9">相撞</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e10"><Object sid="s10">轿车</Object>当场<Denoter type="action" did="d10">翻</Denoter>下<Location lid="l10">路侧沟中</Location></Event>，
                <Event eid="e11"><Denoter type="action" did="d11">撞上</Denoter>路旁一村民的<Object oid="o11">房屋</Object></Event>。</Sentence>
                <Sentence><Event eid="e12">在<Denoter  type="emergency" did="d12">此次交通事故</Denoter></Event>中，造成<Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">两人</Participant>当场<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d13">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">1人</Participant>在<Denoter type="movement" did="d14">送</Denoter><Location lid="l14">医院</Location></Event>
                <Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="operation" did="d15">抢救</Denoter>无效</Event>后
                <Event eid="e16"><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d16">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e17">而<Participant sid="s17">轿车驾驶员</Participant>和<Participant sid="s17">车上一名乘客</Participant>以及<Participant sid="s17">一村民</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d17">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e18">接到<Denoter type="action" did="d18">报案</Denoter></Event>后，<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19，s20，s21，s22">民警</Participant>在最短时间内<Denoter type="movement" did="d19">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l19">现场</Location></Event>
                <Event eid="e20">全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d20">组织</Denoter></Event>
                <Event eid="e21"><Denoter  type="operation" did="d21">抢救</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e22">并将<Participant sid="s22">伤者</Participant><Denoter type="movement" did="d22">送至</Denoter><Location  type="destination" lid="l22">程海卫生院</Location></Event>
                <Event eid="e23"><Denoter type="operation" did="d23">救治</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
                <Sentence><Event eid="e24"><Participant sid="s24">相关领导</Participant>率队<Denoter  type="action" did="d">组成</Denoter><Object oid="o24，s25，s26">“7・10”特大事故处理工作领导小组</Object></Event>，
                <Event eid="e25">分头<Denoter type="operation" did="d25">组织</Denoter>指挥</Event>
                <Event eid="e26"><Denoter type="operation" did="d26">抢救</Denoter><Participant sid="s26">伤员</Participant></Event>等工作。</Sentence><Sentence>目前，伤者病情稳定，
                <Event eid="e27"><Object sid="s27">死者遗体安葬事宜</Object>已妥善<Denoter type="operation" did="d27">解决</Denoter></Event>，死者家属情绪稳定。</Sentence>
                <Sentence><Event eid="e28"><Object oid="o28">事故原因</Object>正在进一步<Denoter type="operation" did="d28">调查</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
